channel.title: What can I cook
channel.description:
My meal plan ran out and I have three days left in the semester. In my possession I currently have canned cheese, three sleeves of crackers, one box of mike n'ikes, half a jug of protein powder, two packs of ramen noodles, three sugar cookies, and a quarter bottle of vodka.
What can I cook with this? All recipes must be microwave safe.
